User enters integer input
play_input -> n -> int(n) -> i -> print(Odd) -> print('Program ends..')


User enter non integer input
play_input -> n -> int(n) -> ValueError (object) -> python process -> print details of the error

User enter non integer input (handling the error)
play_input -> n -> int(n) -> ValueError (object) -> play_input -> print details of the error -> print('Program ends..')